# Under an oak tree, I dried myself #

1125
01:56:00,200 --> 01:56:06,400
# On the highest branch, a
nightingale was singing #

1126
01:56:07,200 --> 01:56:13,800
# So long I've been loving you,
I will never forget you #

1127
01:56:14,800 --> 01:56:20,100
# Sing, nightingale, sing,
your heart is so happy #

1128
01:56:20,200 --> 01:56:26,300
# Your heart feels like laughing,
mine feels like weeping #

1129
01:56:26,400 --> 01:56:27,699
What are you doing?

1130
